solution: 

    private void useRegistryForConfigIfNecessary() {
        registries.stream().filter(RegistryConfig::isZookeeperProtocol).findFirst().ifPresent(rc -> {
            // we use the loading status of DynamicConfiguration to decide whether ConfigCenter has been initiated.
            Environment.getInstance().getDynamicConfiguration().orElseGet(() -> {
                ConfigManager configManager = ConfigManager.getInstance();
                ConfigCenterConfig cc = configManager.getConfigCenter().orElse(new ConfigCenterConfig());
                if (rc.getParameters() != null) {
                    Map<String, String> configParams = cc.getParameters() == null ? new HashMap<>() : cc.getParameters();
                    configParams.putAll(rc.getParameters());
                    cc.setParameters(configParams);
                }
                
                
                if (cc.getParameters() != null) {
                    cc.getParameters().put(org.apache.dubbo.remoting.Constants.CLIENT_KEY,rc.getClient());
                }

//                cc.getParameters().put(org.apache.dubbo.remoting.Constants.CLIENT_KEY,rc.getClient());

                cc.setProtocol(rc.getProtocol());
                cc.setAddress(rc.getAddress());
                cc.setUsername(rc.getUsername());
                cc.setPassword(rc.getPassword());
                cc.setHighestPriority(false);
                setConfigCenter(cc);
                startConfigCenter();
                return null;
            });
        });
    }

> ApplicationEventPublisherAware接口在spring环境下会由ApplicationContextAwareProcessor进行处理的
1.我是从2.6.4版本升级到2.6.5版本之后出现的问题；
2.使用了AnnotationBean扫描了Package，在其中注入了annotationPackage和applicationContext属性；
3.AnnotationBean里面的方法postProcessAfterInitialization在扫描到dubbo的@Service注解后，初始化一个ServiceBean之后进行export();
```java
    /**
     * @since 2.6.5
     */
    @Override
    public void export() {
        super.export();
        // Publish ServiceBeanExportedEvent
        publishExportEvent();
    }
    /**
     * @since 2.6.5
     */
    private void publishExportEvent() {
        ServiceBeanExportedEvent exportEvent = new ServiceBeanExportedEvent(this);
        applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(exportEvent);
    }
```
4.方法里面的applicationEventPublisher这个为Null，导致抛出了空指针异常；
5.ServiceBean实现了ApplicationEventPublisherAware，但是在应用启动的时候并没有执行它的方法
```java
/**
     * @param applicationEventPublisher
     * @since 2.6.5
     */
    @Override
    public void setApplicationEventPublisher(ApplicationEventPublisher applicationEventPublisher) {
        this.applicationEventPublisher = applicationEventPublisher;
    }
```
6.自己调试了一下代码，发现ApplicationContextAwareProcessor在初始化的时候，没有扫描到ServiceBean类型；
7.麻烦大佬帮忙看一下，这个问题已经困惑自己三四天了，目前暂时没有找到解决方案，只能降低版本到2.6.4；

